Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:36.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}像是被湿润的风推搡着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:41.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}你看  我们相遇了
