Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.95,0:00:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是超级大作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天忙到很晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.09,0:00:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得静不下心来  所以打算去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山的试镜日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:00:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责画封面的作家病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近菜花庄的人气也不断攀升
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊  能不能拜托你现在开始画封面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彩色的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彩色…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  彩色的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得黄色的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单色的话  虽然单色很前卫 但是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是封面啊  是决胜的关键啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决胜  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只说了走好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说些更有意义的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名  差不多该起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然自己做了准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是时尚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是袜子却只找到一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是会自动配对的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面不会空空如也吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内裤穿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿了有好多颜色的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:01:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要告诉我细节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那书包里面的东西也给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看女生的包什么的太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是忘带东西了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面放了很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很重要的东西是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很用心的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道怎么回事  不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不看了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要继续追问下去就不礼貌了哦  空太
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么突然过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你通知一下的话我们就去接你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有联系…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  最近虽然忙于课题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是挤出时间来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于女生来说可是决胜的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想慢慢享受和真白的再会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这晚些时候再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你跑掉的  龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}为什么  为什么你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  我们先去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田呢  神田！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}龙之介真是啦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:55.90,SPEC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(344,40)\fs10\frz-14}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:55.90,SPEC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(271,77)\fs11\frz-14}今天我要去了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山  你不是去试镜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下课之后也来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有理由翘课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得不知道该说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我也不期待神田君能好好说些鼓励我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…神田君已经给我勇气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇气？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君向我证明了努力是会有回报的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君  你还记得我们的约定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试镜结束之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  空太  七海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫原
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可听说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你要试镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托啦  七海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是普通科的新星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  宫原同学你太夸张了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力的词源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}原来是指印第奥墨西哥的苦水名为「chocolatl」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.10,SPEC4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(60,275)\fs28}放学后，屋顶上等你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.10,SPEC4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,55)}椎名真白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}所以  大家可不能送巧克力给喜欢的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}虽然尝起来很甜  原本可是很苦的水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面放了重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名是要给我巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你差不多该给我放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般像我这么可爱的女孩子主动倒贴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生应该都会很高兴的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙之介到底不喜欢我什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之请你收下巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过我不会收的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答应了你一个要求  后面就不知道会有多少个要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把人家说得像是恐怖分子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是有过之而无不及啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:07:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞夜的时候  收到你的邮件我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是像年中年末正月的问候一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人可是很讲礼貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有别的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  今天到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是值日生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…青山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在樱花庄里也经常被使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校也是一样的待遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  学弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是要给仁学长的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年生没有硬性规定要来学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我跟宗一郎说好叫他带仁过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  所以我在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看你好像做了很多的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这巧克力还真小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？果然不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话就不能传达我的爱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…倒是觉得你很用心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给他吧  美咲学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲有个不错的学弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒的学弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名  在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊  神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 不好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一下 发生什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车停住了  说是发生了人身事故
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什么时候才会开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点青山  你和养成学校联系了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他们说一下情况应该能理解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了  不过对方说就算时间可以延迟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是日期是不能改的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果六点之前不到的话  别人也都试镜结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山  你现在在哪个车站
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在附近的车站
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能离开电车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  现在是在月台打给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就在检票口附近等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名  我要晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在暂时无法接电话  请在发信音响后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会晚点到  青山遇到困难了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天很冷  在教室里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  是空太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫原  自行车借我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山的电车停了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天试镜  在附近的车站
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  坐上来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫原？不…你只要借我就行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话少说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…禁止骑车带人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下回来让你唠叨的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就先放过我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫原  换我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我好好尝尝爱的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  宫原  爱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更正  是丧家犬的爱的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被七海甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？等等  被甩了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞奔吧  空太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海遇到最大的危机时找的可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山  快点用这个叫部出租车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  大家都想坐出租车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以暂时没有车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…自行车会赶不上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你努力了两年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说好一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起追寻梦想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在这种地方一个人掉队了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请带我去试镜会场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到了飞机起飞的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近真的没有时间  可只有今天很想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请代我告诉樱花庄的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连招呼也没来得及和她们打  真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也替我对真白说声抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P.S.  在机场的吻是我的初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  皓皓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么冷的天还让你陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  还不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我联系一下宗一郎君让他打电话给三鹰君…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多可以进攻的机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  为了感谢你陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请你吃包子吧！  包子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是肉包还是豆沙包  就算是披萨包也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就赶紧让我们吃包子去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}向包子进发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的事…之前好像也有过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要来对对台词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑车的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难听到对方的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会发出很响亮的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个不错的发声练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君  总是那么的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然说有事要和我说  是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还是蛮重要的事…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他总会靠近我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事一直想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很逼真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊…怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里过去已经很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来赶的上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名还在等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了  脚好酸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后冲刺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:16:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…她还在等我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名  抱歉  我晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太总是马上就爽约
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人的时候叫我真白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  真白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹笋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节是巧克力之日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也可以等回了樱花庄再给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要像正常人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多女孩子是在屋顶上给的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫乃给我的漫画里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是正常人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以最近不明白空太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话不该你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太和优子关系好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她是我妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那七海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天空太也去了七海那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事是当然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天对青山来说是非常重要的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说也是重要的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有对我说  一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你已经是专业的了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我们更…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名一直跑在很前面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至看不到她的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  不只是我看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回过头来的椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也看不到我的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实也很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能拿到巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上课收到短信开始我就等不及放学了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力让你很高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是竹笋派的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能感冒了  我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能牵你的手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为静不下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扑通扑通的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…一直都那么遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会扑通扑通的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我们活着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比真白更有活着的感觉
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我已经尽我所能了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  要开饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上井草学姐说是情人节饺子宴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么情人节要吃饺子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤坂君也被硬拉去包饺子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原寄宿女的话她已经回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔来过啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有留住她啊  小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像很忙  那也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可她特意到日本来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事吧  赤坂君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  每个人都有一两件说不出口的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔肯定很快就会再来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  先美美地吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  给仁学长的巧克力到底给他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算再怎么亲近  也有说不出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.14,0:22:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山今天早上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君  你还记得我们的约定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试镜要是通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:22:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山对我…什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.83,0:23:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是甜还是咸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.93,0:23:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放了巧克力的饺子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.07,0:23:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白  你中奖了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈没有告诉你不要用食物来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有好好地放大蒜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,0:23:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节饺子就是这货啊…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙里有很多闪耀的星星大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及很多暗物质
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法说出口的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  我现在有好好地在闪耀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
